    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/99093c82c5f44127c9756bf7fb16fb8b.poster.avif?t=1746810104\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/99093c82c5f44127c9756bf7fb16fb8b.webm?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/99093c82c5f44127c9756bf7fb16fb8b.mp4?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>《克罗艾的镇魂曲 -encore-》是一款充满解密和恐怖要素的日本典型的2D恐怖探险游戏。受到《魔女之家》和《青鬼》等同类型作品的启发，当时还只有十几岁的游戏创作者制作了原版游戏。<br>本作在2013年首次发布的原版的基础上，对游戏画面和音乐进行了全面更新，相信新老玩家都能收获焕然一新的游戏体验。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/261634289ef25841f07be7e49be39e4e.poster.avif?t=1746810104\" width=600 height=100 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/261634289ef25841f07be7e49be39e4e.webm?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/261634289ef25841f07be7e49be39e4e.mp4?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/25eca46720cdec7dbcba904c9de9415c.poster.avif?t=1746810104\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/25eca46720cdec7dbcba904c9de9415c.webm?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>通过豪华的立绘呈现了小提琴家米歇尔和钢琴家克罗艾的对话。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/2eb9dc9477ba4d66837621d6bf56f20e.poster.avif?t=1746810104\" width=600 height=337 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/2eb9dc9477ba4d66837621d6bf56f20e.webm?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>为了解开分散在公馆内的诅咒，玩家需要在左右手上装备不同的道具。同时，也有需要利用简单的音乐相关知识破解的诅咒，“音乐”即是本作的一条重要的主轴。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/baf81d124e44e2777e10cdc216628142.poster.avif?t=1746810104\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/baf81d124e44e2777e10cdc216628142.webm?t=1746810104\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br>以19世纪的西方为主题的世界观，为玩家呈现复古的建筑和内部装饰。<br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2320500/extras/fe9e97a36b6515c32c15d32ec6cbd553.avif?t=1746810104\" width=600 height=156 /></span><br>全体制作人员携游戏角色都欢迎您的光临～",
